Introduction

BF is a South Korean boy group that was previously known as BOYFRIEND. The group, which originally consisted of six members, was formed by Starship Entertainment and made their debut on May 26, 2011, with their first single "Boyfriend". In May 2019, Starship Entertainment announced that the group had disbanded following the expiration of their contracts. However, on April 30, 2021, it was revealed that the group had reunited and would now be known as BF.
